Name: Motorola Moto Edge Plus 2020 12GB Ram 256GB Rom Single Sim PTA Approved
Specifications: ['Introducing the cutting-edge technology and exquisite design of the Motorola Moto Edge Plus 2020, now available with an impressive 12GB RAM and a capacious 256GB ROM, all wrapped up in a sleek single SIM configuration. This device has been officially approved by the PTA, ensuring seamless connectivity and usage in Pakistan.', '*Unleash Boundless Performance:*Experience the future of mobile performance with the Motorola Moto Edge Plus. With its whopping 12GB of RAM, multitasking becomes a breeze, allowing you to effortlessly switch between apps, stream videos, play games, and more. Say goodbye to slowdowns and hello to unrivaled speed.', '*Ample Storage for Your Digital World:*Capture every moment, download your favorite apps, and store your memories without compromise. The 256GB of internal storage offers ample room for all your photos, videos, and files. Never worry about running out of space again.', "*Stunning Display:*Immerse yourself in the vibrant 6.7-inch OLED display that curves elegantly at the edges. With a resolution that's nothing short of breathtaking, you'll enjoy stunning visuals with deep blacks and vibrant colors, making your entertainment and browsing experience truly exceptional.", "*Capture Life in Detail:*The Motorola Moto Edge Plus boasts a sophisticated triple-camera system that lets you capture life's moments with incredible detail and clarity. The 108MP main sensor delivers sharp and vibrant photos, while the ultra-wide lens expands your perspective, and the telephoto lens brings your subjects closer, even from a distance.", "*Long-lasting Battery:*Equipped with a robust 5,000mAh battery, the Moto Edge Plus ensures you stay powered up throughout the day and beyond. Whether you're streaming, gaming, or working, you'll have the freedom to do more without constantly searching for a power outlet.", 'Blazing-Fast Connectivity:Stay connected like never before with 5G capabilities. Enjoy lightning-fast download and upload speeds, seamless video conferencing, and buffer-free streaming. The Motorola Moto Edge Plus makes lag a thing of the past.', "*Sleek Design:*Designed to impress, the Moto Edge Plus features a sleek and modern design that's not only visually striking but also ergonomic. The waterfall display seamlessly merges with the metal and glass body, creating a device that's as comfortable to hold as it is stylish.", '*PTA Approved:*Rest easy knowing that the Motorola Moto Edge Plus 2020 is officially approved by the PTA, ensuring compliance with all regulatory standards in Pakistan. You can enjoy a hassle-free connection experience without any concerns.', 'Elevate your smartphone experience with the Motorola Moto Edge Plus 2020. With its powerful performance, stunning display, exceptional camera system, and PTA approval, this device is the epitome of innovation and reliability. Get ready to explore new horizons in mobile technology.']

Specifications: ['Sparx has launched the budget Neo 5 Plus smartphone on themarket.', 'The Neo 5 Plus comes with some amazing features like 3GB of RAM,a 5000mAh battery, a dual camera setup, and a massive display.', 'It also comes with a fingerprint scanner for added security.', 'It is expected that this new model will be a game changer for the brand with its jaw dropping featuresand specifications.', 'The recently introducedSparx Neo 5 Plus is powered by the well-known Octa Core CPU, which will make ita super fast handset when compared to other Neo series handsets.', "With this Sparx Neo's 5Plus, users will be able to enjoy 3 GB of RAM as well as 64GB of internalstorage.", 'A dedicated memorycard slot will also beavailable to expand the memory of the phone in case of need.', "Because of its enormoussize, Sparx's Neo 5 Plus boasts a huge 6.56-inch IPS LCD capacitive touchscreen display that gives the phone a very premium look due to its massivesize.", 'As well as that, thereis an 8 MP selfie camera hidden under the notch on the front of the phone, the Sparx Neo 5Plus, to capture our beautiful moments in high quality.', 'It has a dual camerasetup on the back that consists of a 13MP + AI lens sensor combination in orderto provide the user with a fantastic photography experience.', 'The huge 5000 mAhbattery will not let down this Neo 5 Plus by Sparx throughout the entire day,even if you only charge it once a day.', 'Further, there is noconfirmation yet about the fast charging support.']

Name: INFINIX SMART 7 4GB RAM 64GB ROM || 6000mAh BATTERY || 4G LTE || 6.6" DISPLAY || ONE YEAR BRAND WARRANTY || PTA APPROVED
Specifications: ["DETAILS OF INFINIX SMART 7 4GB RAM 64GB ROM.Infinix is near to launch Smart 7 series of smartphones and it has been suggested that the devices may be launched in the upcoming months of this year, based on recent leaks.Then let's move on to the latest features of the Infinix Smart 7.Topping the list of features is a dual-lens camera setup, a 6.6-inch full-HD+ display, and a massive 6000 mAh battery with fast charging.In light of the fact that the smartphone might be launched with a massive 6000mAh battery pack, it is likely that users of this phone will be able to use it all day long on a single charge.Furthermore this Infinix Smart 7's a powerful Helio A22 SoC chipset with a couple of Octa-core CPUs.A dedicated memory card slot will enable users to expand the cell phone's memory up to 256GB in addition to the smartphone's 64GB of internal storage.", "There is no doubt that the Infinix Smart 7 is very attractive due to its dual camera setup along with its attractive design.The phone's primary camera sensor is 13 MP, while the second is a 0.3 MP macro sensor.There is a single 5MP camera with an LED flashlight located on the front of the device.The brand new Infinix Smart's 7 is packed with a bigger 6.6 Inches TFT LCD display that can easily support the HD resolution of 720 x 1612 Pixels beside them it offers 500 nits of extra brightness.The improved display of the Infinix Smart's 7 allows for richer and more vibrant colours, greater clarity and better visibility in direct sunlight, making it an ideal device for watching movies, playing games, and browsing the web.The improved brightness also ensures that users will be able to use the device more comfortably in direct sunlight and other bright environments."]
